# Code of Conduct

We expect all contributors and users of this project to respect and adhere to the following code of conduct:

- Be respectful and inclusive to all individuals, regardless of their background or identity.
- Refrain from any form of harassment, discrimination, or offensive behavior.
- Exercise empathy and consider the perspectives of others.
- Stay constructive and focused on discussions related to the project.
- Respect the decisions of project maintainers.

If anyone violates this code of conduct, appropriate actions will be taken, which may include warnings or the removal of contributions or users.

Please report any behavior that violates this code of conduct to [Your Contact Email or Other Contact Information].
